{"tid":2444684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特區政府：絕不認同 歐盟香港年度報告 對《香港國安法》的偏頗和無理政治抹黑，批評歐盟的攻擊明顯是雙重標準。","createTime":"2021-03-13T04:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T04:35:11.000Z","uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"714800ca8fe73ddf0a588461077874cb04508509","tid":2444684,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:21:04.000Z","msg":"歐盟發表香港政治和經濟發展年度報告，外交和安全政策高級代表博雷利指《香港國安法》被用來鎮壓民主力量、扼殺異見和多元化，香港人行使權利和自由產生寒蟬效應，又質疑中國是否願意按一國兩制原則和基本法。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府強烈反對報告的言論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580383-20210313.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580383-20210313.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI6Zg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=0dc653af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580383-20210313.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=23c3f7f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580383-20210313.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5faa10b12d20ba419b127659d8c401b041ef621d","tid":2444684,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:21:29.000Z","msg":"特區政府說，絕不認同報告對《香港國安法》的偏頗和無理政治抹黑，批評歐盟的攻擊明顯是雙重標準。<br />\n<br />\n報告指《香港國安法》對香港市民行使其權利和自由產生寒蟬效應，特區政府反駁是錯誤與偏頗，強調奉公守法的人不會誤墮法網。"},{"pid":"89075e6b05050c9ba33582ae191cdb4cd2f54bf9","tid":2444684,"uid":182519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:21:40.000Z","msg":"anything new?"},{"pid":"97340a5888c7144a598d747f5c9e6f37505a6814","tid":2444684,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"報告質疑中央政府是否仍然貫徹落實「一國兩制」，特區政府認為這是完全沒有根據的指控。"},{"pid":"8ab83662e307ab277accd80c785db496a6c0caa1","tid":2444684,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:22:56.000Z","msg":"是撚旦啦<br />\nHK's Illusionist"},{"pid":"81d1f47a14f028a1cf2cfae5d1c1213dc1f6c5dd","tid":2444684,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:23:49.000Z","msg":"又會咁岩全世界都黑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1b68c476055992c40ab5854106c7ba9a847582","tid":2444684,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81d1f47a14f028a1cf2cfae5d1c1213dc1f6c5dd","tid":2444684,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:23:49.000Z","msg":"又會咁岩全世界都黑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}